snippet.title: SpongeBob Atlantis SquareOff: Map 1 - Bikini Bottom
snippet.description:
SpongeBob's Atlantis SquarePantis SquareOff Video Game for PC, iPad, iPhone, Android and Mac | Map 1: Bikini Bottom
Full game playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPkbvMyUKzFWxzF4WP4z5bmho0gLA8FkB
SpongeBob Atlantis Squarepantis SquareOff: Undersea world of SpongeBob SquarePants, Patrick Star, Mr. Krabs, Plankton, Squidward, Sandy Cheeks, Man Ray, Atlantean Guards and Dirty Bubble! SpongeBob journeys across the ocean floor facing down enemies and collecting cards to build the ultimate deck! Help SpongeBob stop Plankton`s army and free the underwater metropolis
